# Installing Trac on mac OS

- [https://trac.edgewall.org/wiki/TracOnOsx](https://trac.edgewall.org/wiki/TracOnOsx#InstallingusingMacPorts/)

## Start with updating

```bash
sudo port -v selfupdate
sudo port upgrade outdated
```

Install SCM

```bash
sudo port install bazaar subversion git mercurial cvs
```

## Install ruby and rails
```bash
sudo port install ruby24
sudo port select ruby ruby24
sudo port install rb-rubygems
sudo port install rbenv ruby-build
```
